1
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:40,960
Do you want to tell me anything?

2
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:44,440
<i>Your person took mine.</i>

3
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:46,360
<i>Tell Taiga not to mess with Rin.</i>

4
00:02:46,440 --> 00:02:48,600
What if they both want to be together?

5
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:50,840
Uncle! Hey, Uncle!

6
00:02:50,920 --> 00:02:55,040
Indhorn, I'll have to visit
you sometime, cousin.

7
00:02:55,120 --> 00:02:56,320
Rin!

8
00:03:06,960 --> 00:03:09,600
Aru, is there any way for us to get in?

9
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:12,200
Without orders from Techut,

10
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:13,840
no one can enter the lab.

11
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:16,040
We can't wait.

12
00:03:16,120 --> 00:03:19,000
If Rin is sick, Taiga could catch it.

13
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:23,240
I'll try to find a way.

14
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:25,800
Hurry.

15
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:29,840
Once Techut knows the workers are ill,
he'll want to experiment even more.

16
00:03:31,920 --> 00:03:33,840
What exactly is he planning to do?

17
00:03:34,880 --> 00:03:37,760
3C Corp. is building wealth
on people's lives,

18
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:40,800
stepping over corpses to get richer.

19
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:46,840
You know Rin didn't go visit relatives.

20
00:03:48,720 --> 00:03:50,560
You know where she went, who she was with,

21
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:53,920
yet you didn't call her back.

22
00:03:57,160 --> 00:03:58,480
I don't know.

23
00:03:59,880 --> 00:04:01,080
Naruban.

24
00:04:02,640 --> 00:04:05,880
Fire Phoenix has been protecting
your life and your family all along.

25
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:09,240
I don't know where Rin is.

26
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:11,760
I didn't ask,

27
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:16,760
because everyone's already suspicious
about how Rin can work so close to me.

28
00:04:24,440 --> 00:04:26,480
What can 3C-Coin do,

29
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:30,880
besides putting profit
in the hands of your incompetent son?

30
00:04:30,960 --> 00:04:34,280
I did everything Fire Phoenix ordered,

31
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:36,480
created the coin, built the app.

32
00:04:37,400 --> 00:04:40,160
Create pathogens, sell vaccines,

33
00:04:40,880 --> 00:04:42,120
produce medicine.

34
00:04:45,280 --> 00:04:49,000
There's no investment more valuable
than investing in human lives.

35
00:04:50,760 --> 00:04:53,080
Techut is doing everything in the lab.

36
00:04:55,520 --> 00:04:58,600
The pathogens spread
through ingestion or contact,

37
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:02,680
destroying the immune system.

38
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:05,280
Those infected,

39
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:08,880
any weak part fails faster.

40
00:05:09,880 --> 00:05:13,040
Then we produce medicine
that supposedly cures it,

41
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:15,520
vaccines that supposedly prevent it.

42
00:05:17,440 --> 00:05:21,040
Control the world with the diseases
we created ourselves.

43
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:28,280
When will it be done?

44
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:30,600
I've been waiting forever.

45
00:05:31,960 --> 00:05:34,720
If you can't wait, then just kill me.

46
00:05:35,520 --> 00:05:39,240
Fire Phoenix has my life in their hands.
Do whatever you want.

47
00:05:39,840 --> 00:05:41,120
You're daring,

48
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:45,720
because you know
only you can command 3C Corp.,

49
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:49,280
without relying on Prin or Chanchai.

50
00:05:50,840 --> 00:05:54,800
Fire Phoenix has held my friends
and family hostage from the start.

51
00:05:54,880 --> 00:05:57,640
If you think I'm useless, go ahead.

52
00:05:57,720 --> 00:06:01,680
A life worse than death,
maybe it can finally end.

53
00:06:02,880 --> 00:06:04,160
You're daring,

54
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:08,040
because you know Fire Phoenix
needs 3C Corp. as a nominee.

55
00:06:08,680 --> 00:06:10,880
I stay under Fire Phoenix's shadow

56
00:06:10,960 --> 00:06:13,200
because my wife and children's lives
are the most important.

57
00:06:13,280 --> 00:06:16,400
What about other families?
Are they just bait?

58
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:20,080
That's exactly how you think.
That's why you took Rin in,

59
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:23,440
even though you killed her father,
your own senior!

60
00:06:44,400 --> 00:06:47,360
Dad!

61
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:03,120
Mr. Naruban.

62
00:07:03,840 --> 00:07:05,560
Everyone has wounds.

63
00:07:06,440 --> 00:07:09,360
If you don't want old scars reopened,
don't threaten me.

64
00:07:11,640 --> 00:07:14,240
Fire Phoenix wants to control this world.

65
00:07:14,320 --> 00:07:16,600
But I just want to protect my family.

66
00:07:52,480 --> 00:07:56,240
Our 3C Group is number one now,
thanks to our satellite.

67
00:07:58,040 --> 00:08:00,640
That costs a fortune.

68
00:08:01,440 --> 00:08:02,560
But it's worth it.

69
00:08:03,960 --> 00:08:06,120
If we want to own this world,

70
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:08,440
we need money. Money is power.

71
00:08:12,280 --> 00:08:15,360
Right now, everyone is supporting us.

72
00:08:15,440 --> 00:08:17,440
The MP is fully clearing the way.

73
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:22,920
And what do we have to give in return?

74
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:25,560
Full support,

75
00:08:25,640 --> 00:08:27,600
to make him the leader in the House.

76
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:32,440
Are you sure, Prin?

77
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:35,919
What if we pick a side
and the power shifts?

78
00:08:39,799 --> 00:08:43,200
Power will never shift.
Fire Phoenix has our back.

79
00:08:49,760 --> 00:08:51,560
Who is this Fire Phoenix?

80
00:08:51,640 --> 00:08:53,560
How do they have so much power?

81
00:08:53,640 --> 00:08:56,560
Fire Phoenix is a secret organization
set to change this world.

82
00:08:57,520 --> 00:09:00,720
Whether it's economy, politics, or food,

83
00:09:00,800 --> 00:09:03,240
the power of every network in the world

84
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:06,560
has long been controlled
by the minds of Fire Phoenix.

85
00:09:08,160 --> 00:09:09,640
Ministers,

86
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:12,680
MPs, business tycoons,

87
00:09:12,760 --> 00:09:14,680
bank owners,

88
00:09:14,760 --> 00:09:16,320
and some academics,

89
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:19,400
they're the key members of Fire Phoenix.

90
00:09:23,680 --> 00:09:26,840
Our business shouldn't get involved
with these secret organizations.

91
00:09:26,920 --> 00:09:28,040
We have to.

92
00:09:29,320 --> 00:09:31,000
Technology is changing the world.

93
00:09:31,640 --> 00:09:33,040
If it's in our hands,

94
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:35,360
why let the opportunity slip?

95
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:37,280
Right, Chanchai?

96
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:39,280
Yes.

97
00:09:40,560 --> 00:09:43,680
Our software can shrink the world
to fit in your hands.

98
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:50,000
Trust me.

99
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:52,600
Believe in me.

100
00:09:54,960 --> 00:09:58,800
Only the brave can change the world.

101
00:10:08,240 --> 00:10:09,320
Here it is.

102
00:10:09,400 --> 00:10:11,040
Smells amazing!

103
00:10:12,640 --> 00:10:15,520
It's hot right out of the oven.

104
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:17,760
Your roasted chicken is my favorite.

105
00:10:18,800 --> 00:10:21,080
I'll take the first piece, if that's okay.

106
00:10:21,160 --> 00:10:22,320
- Sure.
- Of course.

107
00:10:22,400 --> 00:10:23,480
Thank you.

108
00:10:25,480 --> 00:10:27,240
I'll give you the biggest piece.

109
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:28,840
- Here.
- Thank you.

110
00:10:30,760 --> 00:10:33,920
Ma'am, a guest is here to see you.

111
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:39,720
It's Khanin.

112
00:10:40,680 --> 00:10:43,880
He arranged to meet me.
I almost forgot too.

113
00:10:45,840 --> 00:10:47,000
Excuse me for a moment.

114
00:11:00,800 --> 00:11:02,600
I have something to tell you.

115
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:14,800
I'm warning you as an old friend.

116
00:11:14,880 --> 00:11:15,920
About what?

117
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:24,920
Our profit this year has exceeded 200%.

118
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:27,360
Our satellite is about to go online.

119
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:29,240
What else are you worried about, Prin?

120
00:11:29,320 --> 00:11:31,440
Someone wants our customer data.

121
00:11:31,520 --> 00:11:33,480
Hey, are you crazy?

122
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:36,680
Customer data is top secret.
Who would want it?

123
00:11:42,200 --> 00:11:43,360
Fire Phoenix.

124
00:11:51,480 --> 00:11:55,760
Fire Phoenix helped us win
the satellite bid for our customer data?

125
00:11:55,840 --> 00:11:58,920
At first, I thought
they just wanted money and some shares.

126
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:02,640
Didn't expect them
to want our customer data too.

127
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:06,200
Hey, if our customer data leaks,

128
00:12:06,280 --> 00:12:07,840
our business is finished, Prin.

129
00:12:07,920 --> 00:12:10,560
Our reputation, credibility,

130
00:12:10,640 --> 00:12:12,440
our technology,

131
00:12:12,520 --> 00:12:16,320
other shareholders, the media,
everything will come crashing down on us.

132
00:12:21,880 --> 00:12:23,000
I can't give it.

133
00:12:24,640 --> 00:12:25,760
Someone warned me.

134
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:27,720
If Fire Phoenix gets our customer data,

135
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:29,840
3C Corp. will be meaningless.

136
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:34,400
And if we don't give it,

137
00:12:35,920 --> 00:12:37,240
will it be dangerous?

138
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:39,600
We'll have to take a stand.

139
00:12:40,320 --> 00:12:42,480
You be careful.

140
00:12:43,280 --> 00:12:44,920
I'll warn Chanchai too.

141
00:12:53,840 --> 00:12:54,680
Prin.

142
00:12:57,160 --> 00:12:58,600
I'm sorry, my friend.

143
00:13:00,840 --> 00:13:03,040
I have to be Fire Phoenix's puppet.

144
00:13:04,280 --> 00:13:07,120
Because I can't let my family die
the way you did.

145
00:13:31,120 --> 00:13:32,160
Rin.

146
00:13:50,360 --> 00:13:51,920
Your body's still hot.

147
00:14:03,240 --> 00:14:04,440
Yours is so cold.

148
00:14:47,880 --> 00:14:49,120
I'm going to 3C Corp.

149
00:14:49,960 --> 00:14:51,560
to get medicine from Techut for you.

150
00:14:56,240 --> 00:14:58,120
- I'll come with you.
- No, Rin.

151
00:14:58,880 --> 00:15:02,040
Stay here. I'm getting
the medicine to treat you.

152
00:15:02,800 --> 00:15:03,640
Taiga.

153
00:15:04,560 --> 00:15:05,960
Don't go this far.

154
00:15:08,040 --> 00:15:08,920
Rin!

155
00:15:16,080 --> 00:15:17,840
You stay here.

156
00:15:18,680 --> 00:15:19,920
Don't let anything happen to you, Rin.

157
00:15:23,360 --> 00:15:26,160
Wait for me until I come back for you.

158
00:15:42,240 --> 00:15:43,560
If you go back to 3C Corp.,

159
00:15:43,640 --> 00:15:46,000
Naruban will never let you go back to Rin.

160
00:15:46,080 --> 00:15:47,840
I'll take the risk.

161
00:15:49,000 --> 00:15:50,800
Rin's condition is getting worse.

162
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:55,520
I should be able to get into the lab
faster than Ratee.

163
00:15:56,840 --> 00:15:58,280
I need to know

164
00:15:58,360 --> 00:16:00,560
what evil plans Fire Phoenix has.

165
00:16:01,840 --> 00:16:03,720
I'll stop them at all costs.

166
00:16:16,880 --> 00:16:18,720
Fire Phoenix.

167
00:16:18,800 --> 00:16:22,160
Honestly, I shouldn't be involved.

168
00:16:23,280 --> 00:16:25,040
But Prae was once my lover

169
00:16:25,120 --> 00:16:27,440
and has always been a good friend.

170
00:16:28,200 --> 00:16:29,480
I also know

171
00:16:30,600 --> 00:16:32,360
she loves her family more than anything.

172
00:16:34,800 --> 00:16:36,400
I have secret info.

173
00:16:36,480 --> 00:16:40,080
Fire Phoenix's planning
to take over your company.

174
00:16:40,160 --> 00:16:41,320
How do you know that?

175
00:16:41,400 --> 00:16:42,600
I'm a cop.

176
00:16:42,680 --> 00:16:45,320
But the info you just shared,

177
00:16:45,400 --> 00:16:48,480
no cop outside Fire Phoenix
would know this.

178
00:16:50,480 --> 00:16:51,840
You're a businessman

179
00:16:51,920 --> 00:16:53,560
who likes taking risks.

180
00:16:53,640 --> 00:16:55,480
But anything involving Fire Phoenix,

181
00:16:55,560 --> 00:16:59,320
Prae and your three young sons
shouldn't be involved or put at risk.

182
00:17:01,360 --> 00:17:02,680
Be careful.

183
00:17:02,760 --> 00:17:05,040
Protect your family.

184
00:17:05,119 --> 00:17:09,119
Don't underestimate Fire Phoenix's people.

185
00:17:17,119 --> 00:17:19,760
Fire Phoenix destroys everyone,

186
00:17:20,920 --> 00:17:22,520
your family,

187
00:17:24,359 --> 00:17:25,720
my family,

188
00:17:27,839 --> 00:17:29,600
and Phumin's family.

189
00:17:30,440 --> 00:17:33,480
The arrests you two made
were excellent work.

190
00:17:33,560 --> 00:17:35,360
The boss was very impressed.

191
00:17:36,520 --> 00:17:37,520
I have a great team.

192
00:17:39,080 --> 00:17:41,320
Don't stop. Keep taking them down.

193
00:17:42,520 --> 00:17:44,920
Destroy all the human trafficking gangs.

194
00:17:46,320 --> 00:17:48,840
If you need to go investigate over there,

195
00:17:48,920 --> 00:17:52,600
just tell me.
I have some allies who can help.

196
00:17:52,680 --> 00:17:53,800
Yes.

197
00:17:56,320 --> 00:17:57,320
- Phumin.
- Huh?

198
00:17:59,040 --> 00:18:00,920
I'll follow your lead.

199
00:18:01,680 --> 00:18:03,440
You can close every major case.

200
00:18:05,760 --> 00:18:07,840
But there are some cases
that remain unsolved.

201
00:18:08,640 --> 00:18:09,760
Really?

202
00:18:11,000 --> 00:18:12,200
Which cases?

203
00:18:13,680 --> 00:18:15,480
The case involving Fire Phoenix.

204
00:18:18,920 --> 00:18:20,800
People have probably forgotten by now,

205
00:18:21,840 --> 00:18:23,600
but I never will.

206
00:18:24,320 --> 00:18:26,640
The family of a famous businessman,

207
00:18:26,720 --> 00:18:28,040
the father was murdered.

208
00:18:29,800 --> 00:18:32,960
And the mother and three young sons

209
00:18:33,840 --> 00:18:36,560
were shot at until their car
plunged into the river.

210
00:18:36,640 --> 00:18:37,840
No one survived.

211
00:18:39,360 --> 00:18:41,120
They were monstrously cruel.

212
00:18:43,000 --> 00:18:45,040
This murder was ordered by Fire Phoenix.

213
00:18:46,200 --> 00:18:48,680
But the authorities don't believe
such an organization exists.

214
00:18:50,640 --> 00:18:53,680
But you have proof for this, right?

215
00:18:54,640 --> 00:18:55,520
I do.

216
00:18:56,560 --> 00:18:59,240
But I still can't link everything,

217
00:18:59,320 --> 00:19:00,880
missing the mastermind's name.

218
00:19:01,640 --> 00:19:05,320
From all my investigations, I'm certain

219
00:19:05,400 --> 00:19:06,880
this organization exists.

220
00:19:09,360 --> 00:19:10,480
But the thing is,

221
00:19:10,560 --> 00:19:14,240
Fire Phoenix's people have infiltrated us.

222
00:19:15,160 --> 00:19:17,200
In a society where powerful people

223
00:19:17,840 --> 00:19:19,240
are corrupt,

224
00:19:20,840 --> 00:19:23,160
even if there are only a handful,

225
00:19:24,080 --> 00:19:27,520
they eat away at the entire system
and the whole country.

226
00:19:30,600 --> 00:19:32,840
The 3C businessman case

227
00:19:33,720 --> 00:19:34,720
has been closed.

228
00:19:35,320 --> 00:19:37,720
The new management continues.

229
00:19:38,520 --> 00:19:41,360
But deep down,

230
00:19:41,440 --> 00:19:43,480
I know the truth was buried.

231
00:19:45,760 --> 00:19:49,040
The criminals walked free
because of power.

232
00:19:51,880 --> 00:19:54,280
You're the new generation of cops.

233
00:19:58,280 --> 00:20:00,760
You must act with integrity

234
00:20:01,680 --> 00:20:04,120
and serve justice for society

235
00:20:04,200 --> 00:20:06,000
and the people as much as you can.

236
00:20:07,080 --> 00:20:08,120
Yes.

237
00:20:09,240 --> 00:20:11,840
- I'm counting on you.
- Yes.

238
00:20:35,120 --> 00:20:37,560
Is there any evidence or trace

239
00:20:38,480 --> 00:20:40,160
linking you…

240
00:20:42,560 --> 00:20:43,720
to Prin's case?

241
00:20:45,480 --> 00:20:46,480
No.

242
00:20:47,400 --> 00:20:50,560
I didn't do it. I don't know.
What else do the police want to ask?

243
00:20:52,800 --> 00:20:54,640
I'm not asking as a cop.

244
00:20:59,560 --> 00:21:03,000
I need to be sure
nothing drags you into this.

245
00:21:03,840 --> 00:21:05,400
If the case isn't reopened,

246
00:21:06,000 --> 00:21:09,000
3C Group will have you
as its leader permanently.

247
00:21:31,640 --> 00:21:34,880
I wanted to freshen up your room,
so I brought some flowers.

248
00:21:47,040 --> 00:21:48,640
I have a meeting in ten minutes.

249
00:21:49,840 --> 00:21:51,840
Thank you for the information,
Inspector Punlop.

250
00:21:57,720 --> 00:21:58,880
Come here.

251
00:22:15,520 --> 00:22:16,800
The Naruban,

252
00:22:18,120 --> 00:22:20,480
Prin, and 3C Group matter was over.

253
00:22:21,800 --> 00:22:25,000
If you hadn't planned to reopen the case,

254
00:22:27,080 --> 00:22:29,200
I wouldn't have to deal
with you like this.

255
00:22:41,400 --> 00:22:42,240
Dad!

256
00:23:32,440 --> 00:23:33,600
Hello, Mrs. Giranun.

257
00:23:35,880 --> 00:23:38,480
You took some time for inspiration.
How was it?

258
00:23:39,880 --> 00:23:40,720
It was good.

259
00:23:41,440 --> 00:23:43,000
Is there anything you want me to do?

260
00:23:43,840 --> 00:23:47,240
I'm going to a charity event.
I'd like to wear one of your designs.

261
00:23:48,480 --> 00:23:49,320
My pleasure.

262
00:23:52,440 --> 00:23:57,520
While you're here, is anything
bothering you or making you uncomfortable?

263
00:23:59,440 --> 00:24:00,360
Not at all.

264
00:24:00,960 --> 00:24:02,400
Very good.

265
00:24:02,480 --> 00:24:04,640
We still have many new projects.

266
00:24:04,720 --> 00:24:07,800
Your perspective
will be valuable for 3C Corp.

267
00:24:08,560 --> 00:24:12,480
We want you to feel happy here,

268
00:24:13,440 --> 00:24:15,040
like part of the family,

269
00:24:16,080 --> 00:24:17,320
the 3C family.

270
00:24:18,680 --> 00:24:19,680
Yes.

271
00:24:25,720 --> 00:24:27,000
Just a moment.

272
00:24:35,880 --> 00:24:37,080
Do you like this design?

273
00:24:57,280 --> 00:24:58,480
Mr. Techut!

274
00:24:59,240 --> 00:25:00,520
Mr. Techut!

275
00:25:03,840 --> 00:25:06,880
This is the report
you asked me to summarize.

276
00:25:11,920 --> 00:25:13,400
This isn't what I ordered.

277
00:25:14,040 --> 00:25:15,280
Oh, really?

278
00:25:16,120 --> 00:25:18,720
I'm sorry. I messed up.

279
00:25:54,200 --> 00:25:55,560
Techut's fingerprints are on this.

280
00:25:55,640 --> 00:25:58,680
Copy it quickly,
so we can get into the lab.

281
00:26:14,840 --> 00:26:16,720
We're really going to get
Techut's prints, right?

282
00:26:19,080 --> 00:26:21,600
- Can you step back a bit?
- You bear, don't joke around!

283
00:26:21,680 --> 00:26:24,440
Yeah, don't joke around.

284
00:26:24,520 --> 00:26:26,560
Your breath is on my cheek.

285
00:26:27,400 --> 00:26:28,840
It gives me the chills.

286
00:26:33,400 --> 00:26:34,480
Is it working?

287
00:26:43,920 --> 00:26:45,000
Is it working?

288
00:26:54,960 --> 00:26:57,760
Am I really that stunning,
you're speechless?

289
00:27:19,720 --> 00:27:21,240
Ms. Rin, don't worry.

290
00:27:22,080 --> 00:27:24,680
If anything happens,
you can call the staff.

291
00:27:30,920 --> 00:27:32,120
Thank you so much.

292
00:27:33,320 --> 00:27:34,920
Mr. Taiga asked me to look after you.

293
00:27:44,800 --> 00:27:48,040
Our pathogen experiment
worked perfectly, Dad.

294
00:27:48,120 --> 00:27:51,080
The workers at Uncle Narumit's farm
got sick immediately.

295
00:27:53,680 --> 00:27:54,920
Why test it there?

296
00:27:56,240 --> 00:27:58,560
It's Uncle's farm. What's the problem?

297
00:27:59,200 --> 00:28:01,480
He's bedridden.

298
00:28:02,240 --> 00:28:03,800
Auntie's always looking after him,

299
00:28:04,400 --> 00:28:06,880
and Indhorn's busy with farm work.

300
00:28:07,640 --> 00:28:09,200
Nobody cares.

301
00:28:09,280 --> 00:28:12,120
Nobody knows what disease

302
00:28:12,200 --> 00:28:13,280
or where it came from.

303
00:28:15,320 --> 00:28:16,440
Did it work well?

304
00:28:17,960 --> 00:28:20,560
It's awesome, Dad!
I've sped up the lab work.

305
00:28:20,640 --> 00:28:22,800
We will have the vaccines ready.

306
00:28:23,440 --> 00:28:26,160
Once people get infected
with this pathogen,

307
00:28:27,200 --> 00:28:28,440
we sell the vaccines.

308
00:28:29,400 --> 00:28:31,080
Later, we sell the medicine.

309
00:28:31,680 --> 00:28:35,120
Paid through 3C-Coin,
they get it fast, they survive.

310
00:28:36,200 --> 00:28:37,560
If treatment is too slow,

311
00:28:40,760 --> 00:28:41,680
they'll die.

312
00:28:48,200 --> 00:28:49,600
Did you get everything ready?

313
00:28:49,680 --> 00:28:50,840
Ready.

314
00:29:24,560 --> 00:29:25,400
‪Hey.

315
00:29:34,720 --> 00:29:36,560
NARUBAN'S HOUSE

316
00:29:53,040 --> 00:29:54,520
Mom, are you checking on Mr. Taiga?

317
00:30:10,080 --> 00:30:13,240
I just like seeing him when he's working.

318
00:30:15,200 --> 00:30:17,560
<i>Today I had lunch with Mr. Taiga.</i>

319
00:30:18,360 --> 00:30:20,640
<i>Really? What did you talk about?</i>

320
00:30:22,840 --> 00:30:24,680
About the coin.

321
00:30:24,760 --> 00:30:26,840
Mr. Taiga will have me teach him.

322
00:30:27,840 --> 00:30:31,160
<i>And he'll teach me about surfing.</i>
<i>We're swapping skills.</i>

323
00:30:32,720 --> 00:30:33,800
<i>That's good.</i>

324
00:30:34,560 --> 00:30:38,160
Well, I'm sleepy. Time for bed.

325
00:30:38,240 --> 00:30:39,080
Good night.

326
00:30:39,960 --> 00:30:41,080
Good night.

327
00:31:25,680 --> 00:31:27,760
- Hey!
- Hey!

328
00:31:27,840 --> 00:31:29,920
Hey!

329
00:31:31,480 --> 00:31:32,400
- Hey!
- Whoa!

330
00:31:50,840 --> 00:31:53,240
FIRE EXIT

331
00:33:42,800 --> 00:33:44,120
The blue bottle is the medicine.

332
00:34:09,600 --> 00:34:11,400
- Hey!
- Oh no!

333
00:34:17,840 --> 00:34:19,080
<i>Taiga.</i>

334
00:34:19,159 --> 00:34:21,400
Only two minutes left. Get out now!

335
00:35:01,360 --> 00:35:03,400
Don't let Taiga leave the 3C building.

336
00:35:17,960 --> 00:35:19,920
SLIDE TO ANSWER

337
00:35:26,280 --> 00:35:27,320
SPEAKER

338
00:35:27,920 --> 00:35:29,200
I know you're listening.

339
00:35:30,920 --> 00:35:33,360
Taiga's being targeted at 3C.

340
00:35:33,960 --> 00:35:35,440
Help him survive.

341
00:36:14,360 --> 00:36:15,480
Rin got the medicine.

342
00:36:17,520 --> 00:36:19,400
Thank you!

343
00:36:20,200 --> 00:36:21,720
Are you tired?

344
00:36:21,800 --> 00:36:23,920
Great job! Amazing!

345
00:36:26,000 --> 00:36:27,160
Is it too hard?

346
00:38:35,880 --> 00:38:37,920
We're Taiga's friends.

347
00:38:50,040 --> 00:38:51,240
Rin!

348
00:38:55,560 --> 00:38:57,280
He gave you the medicine.
How are you doing?

349
00:38:58,720 --> 00:38:59,880
My breathing's easier.

350
00:39:04,280 --> 00:39:07,040
The bruises, the color hasn't darkened.

351
00:39:15,440 --> 00:39:17,360
This is Khanin. He's my friend.

352
00:39:24,800 --> 00:39:26,040
I'll watch over her myself.

353
00:39:37,560 --> 00:39:39,440
I have to get back to 3C Corp.,

354
00:39:40,360 --> 00:39:42,080
or Naruban will get suspicious.

355
00:39:43,400 --> 00:39:44,800
Fire Phoenix is going to get you,

356
00:39:45,960 --> 00:39:48,400
especially if they find out
you took the medicine.

357
00:39:50,560 --> 00:39:52,960
Aru said it's just an experimental drug.

358
00:39:54,280 --> 00:39:55,720
Rin might recover slowly.

359
00:39:58,160 --> 00:39:59,840
But if Rin and I stay here,

360
00:40:00,640 --> 00:40:02,320
the people from 3C will find us,

361
00:40:03,080 --> 00:40:05,440
and Mr. Indhorn will get into trouble too.

362
00:40:06,240 --> 00:40:09,280
But you and Rin
can't just return to 3C easily either.

363
00:40:10,360 --> 00:40:13,360
Punlop won't let you two go.

364
00:40:14,280 --> 00:40:15,120
Punlop.

365
00:40:16,400 --> 00:40:19,360
What if Rin's willing to switch sides
and help you…

366
00:40:22,280 --> 00:40:24,200
I'm not thinking about any of that.

367
00:40:27,200 --> 00:40:28,960
I just want Rin to be safe.

368
00:40:34,640 --> 00:40:35,600
Dhammatat.

369
00:40:37,520 --> 00:40:39,600
Take this to Mr. Indhorn at the office.

370
00:40:40,440 --> 00:40:41,360
Tell him it's medicine for the workers.

371
00:40:53,360 --> 00:40:54,280
Khanin.

372
00:40:56,400 --> 00:40:58,360
How did you manage to help me last night?

373
00:41:00,160 --> 00:41:01,800
Naruban told me.

374
00:41:02,560 --> 00:41:03,480
Naruban?

375
00:41:05,160 --> 00:41:06,680
I traced it.

376
00:41:06,760 --> 00:41:08,480
The number that called was Naruban's.

377
00:41:09,200 --> 00:41:10,920
But I still don't get

378
00:41:11,000 --> 00:41:13,080
why he had me help you.

379
00:41:14,240 --> 00:41:17,520
Maybe he knew
I brought the medicine for Rin.

380
00:41:17,600 --> 00:41:20,960
He could've helped his own staff directly,
no need to go through you.

381
00:41:22,960 --> 00:41:26,000
Still, no one knows Rin's here.

382
00:41:27,480 --> 00:41:28,680
If that's the case,

383
00:41:29,680 --> 00:41:31,160
the Fire Phoenix agents

384
00:41:31,720 --> 00:41:33,960
should've tracked us here already.

385
00:41:35,960 --> 00:41:37,280
Unless,

386
00:41:39,960 --> 00:41:42,520
Rin is another important woman
for Naruban.

387
00:41:44,240 --> 00:41:45,640
Don't touch Rin.

388
00:41:47,160 --> 00:41:50,800
Looks like you're softening
toward Fire Phoenix's people, Taiga.

389
00:41:51,800 --> 00:41:54,080
I'm asking you, Khanin.

390
00:41:54,920 --> 00:41:56,720
Love is changing you.

391
00:41:58,960 --> 00:42:02,400
You care about Fire Phoenix's woman
more than your father's death.

392
00:42:02,480 --> 00:42:05,400
Naruban's doing something
far worse than killing an enemy.

393
00:42:05,480 --> 00:42:08,040
His virus will kill
millions of innocent people.

394
00:42:08,840 --> 00:42:11,240
Rin and the workers are the first victims.

395
00:42:11,880 --> 00:42:14,560
If you don't help stop this evil,

396
00:42:14,640 --> 00:42:16,560
no one can guarantee

397
00:42:18,040 --> 00:42:19,600
you'll survive one day.

398
00:43:00,800 --> 00:43:03,680
I think Aru is trying to steal our data.

399
00:43:12,640 --> 00:43:14,280
Mr. Te.

400
00:43:14,360 --> 00:43:18,360
I'll be right back from the bathroom,
then we can talk.

401
00:43:19,800 --> 00:43:21,120
Mr. Techut!

402
00:43:23,080 --> 00:43:24,160
Want to see a doctor?

403
00:43:56,320 --> 00:43:57,640
We have to go back to 3C Corp.

404
00:43:58,360 --> 00:44:01,160
If we stay any longer,
people will start to get suspicious.

405
00:44:01,240 --> 00:44:03,240
You need to get better first.

406
00:44:07,320 --> 00:44:08,760
For what?

407
00:44:10,040 --> 00:44:11,840
Why are you being good to me?

408
00:44:12,480 --> 00:44:14,200
In the end, we'll have to kill each other.

409
00:44:16,240 --> 00:44:18,320
I want to fight a strong enemy.

410
00:44:19,760 --> 00:44:22,320
It means I'm not winning against the weak.

411
00:44:25,440 --> 00:44:28,680
So you just want to beat me,
you'd do anything for that?

412
00:44:43,240 --> 00:44:44,080
Yes.

413
00:44:45,600 --> 00:44:47,360
Just to be above you.

414
00:45:00,160 --> 00:45:01,840
I want Rin to work with me.

415
00:45:01,920 --> 00:45:03,560
Holding people captive like that,

416
00:45:03,640 --> 00:45:05,840
you could go to jail, Mr. Taiga.

417
00:45:06,440 --> 00:45:08,160
Why are you stopping, Sun?

418
00:45:11,400 --> 00:45:13,960
Anyone who betrays me
must die a painful death.

419
00:45:15,240 --> 00:45:16,280
What are you doing here?

420
00:45:16,360 --> 00:45:18,720
- Just didn't want to say.
- What are you doing here?!

421
00:45:53,960 --> 00:45:56,000
Subtitle translation by:
Chomchanach Yanaharn
